title: 019: Stages of a Woman's Evolvement- Part 1 With Sahara Rose
itunes:title: 019: Stages of a Woman's Evolvement- Part 1 With Sahara Rose
description:
Back from my travels in Formentera, South of France and Mykonos, Greece and couldn't be more excited to be back behind the mic sharing with you. My travels sparked the realization of how much I've changed (in a good way) which is what prompted me to record this episode about the stages of a woman's evolvement. You're invited to my virtual book launch! Register here: https://app.webinarjam.net/live/38070/59d2e51c9f/0/3n139556493xR

Be part of a community that supports you discovering your dharma in Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood collective with community, content, creativity and so much more — learn more about rosegoldgoddesses.com.

Intro + Outro Music: Silent Ganges by Maneesh de Moor
